在远古的维亚德，盛行于世的炼金术极大推动了文明的发展，但是最后，带给世界战乱的炼金术随着尘封而逐渐消失<ref name="agesago">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| version=| level=| language=en| quote='''In-game text:''' Ages ago, or so the stories tell, the power of Alchemy ruled over the world of Weyard. Alchemy wrought the base elements of humanity into thriving civilizations, like lead into gold. But in time, man's dreams gave birth to untold strife. Dreams of endless riches, of eternal life, of dominion over all that lived... Dreams of conquest and war.>}}</ref>。开启炼金术封印的4颗元素之星藏在在阿尔法山的神殿中，由海迪亚村民世世代代的守护着。在《[[黄金太阳_开启的封印|开启的封印]]》中，年轻的海迪亚炼金术士罗宾和杰拉德进入阿尔法山进行探索<ref name="alchemystudy">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Dora:''' Where do you all plan to go today? / '''Garet:''' We're going to Mt. Aleph with Kraden. / '''Dora:''' Mountain climbing with Kraden, eh? Kids and their games... / '''Jenna:''' No! It's part of our studies... / '''Dora:''' Ah, yes... Alchemy.}}</ref>，然而三颗元素之星却被萨帝罗斯、梅娜蒂、加西亚和阿历克斯一行夺走<ref name="sattythreaten">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Saturos:''' You heard us... If you wish to save your friends, then give us the Elemental Stars! / '''Menardi:''' Do you accept our terms? / '''Isaac:''' Yes. / '''Kraden:''' No, Isaac! You must not give them the Elemental Stars! / '''Saturos:''' Why would you deny us? Don't you want your friends to be safe?}}</ref>。在追逐萨帝罗斯点燃水星灯塔期间，另两位年轻的炼金术士伊万<ref name="ivanjoin">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Ivan:''' Your quest has been on my mind ever since I left Vault. Remember? I read everything that happened in your minds. I couldn't just leave, not with all these terrible things happening. If I can't rescue Master Hammet, then I want to help you... Please, allow me to join your quest.}}</ref>和米雅莉<ref name="miajoin">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Mia:''' Well, I... Uh... I... I'll be joining Isaac on his quest.}}</ref>加入队伍，然而罗宾一行却仍没能阻止萨帝罗斯用点燃第一座灯塔<ref name="mercurylit">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Garet:''' It's too late! The lighthouse has already been lit! / '''Mia:''' It... It can't be! The beacon cannot be lit without the Mercury Star...}}</ref>。在漫长的追逐后，罗宾一行和萨帝罗斯等人在金星灯塔再次展开了战斗，萨帝罗斯和梅娜蒂为恢复力量而把金星之星投进了灯塔<ref name="sattylightsbeacon">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Saturos:''' I hope you don't think you've finished us off. / '''Mia:''' You may not be finished, but you can barely stand. / '''Menardi:''' Right now, yes... But we'll be back on our feet... as soon as we do THIS! / '''Saturos:''' (Throws the Venus Star into the Venus Lighthouse well) / '''Ivan:''' Oh, no! He threw the Elemental Star into the lighthouse! / '''Mia:''' How could this happen... We couldn't keep them from lighting the beacon! / '''Saturos:''' That's not all... The energy of the beacon will restore our power.}}</ref>，却依然被罗宾杀掉<ref name="finalvictory">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote= '''Saturos:''' How... How... did we lose? / '''Menardi:''' We are superior in every way, but still we were defeated... }}</ref>。然而加西亚和阿历克斯却依然在继续寻找剩下的两座灯塔<ref name="isitavictory">{{cite video game| title= Golden Sun| developer= Camelot| publisher= Nintendo| date= 2001-11-11| platform=| version=| level=| language= en| quote='''Garet:''' We did it! We won! / '''Ivan:''' We beat them...but have we really won? / '''Isaac:''' Yes. / '''Ivan:''' Even though we couldn't stop the beacon from being lit? / '''Garet:''' What are you talking about? We did everything we could! Sure we couldn't save the Venus Lighthouse, but... We beat them! They're gone! You saw them fall down into the pit... So we don't have to worry about any more beacons being lit! / '''Mia:''' But Felix is gone, and he's taken Sheba... }}</ref>。

在《[[黄金太阳_失落的时代|失落的时代]]》中，玩家将控制加西亚，并继续完成既定的任务——点燃剩下的两座灯塔，让强大的炼金术之力重回维亚德<ref name="manualprologue" />。在罗宾一行寻找加西亚的同时<ref name="isaacasanenemy">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''Jenna:''' Believe me, I'd love to see Isaac again, but we just don't have the time to look for him. Plus... / '''Kraden:''' Even if we did find them, there's a good chance we'd end up fighting them. / '''Piers:''' Why? / '''Kraden:''' What we are trying to achieve, they are trying to prevent... And they will fight to stop us.}}</ref>，加西亚一行也乘坐着新伙伴皮卡德的船扬帆起航。了解到如不让炼金术回归，世界将会面临消亡之后<ref name="truthaboutalchemy">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''Piers:''' However, the world seems even smaller now than it appears on Lunpa's map... / '''Consevato:''' What are you saying? / '''Kraden:''' Time itself has stopped... Think of Weyard as a living, breathing being, possessing its own life force... The four elements are the nourishment needed to sustain this being. / '''Lunpa:''' Kraden... This is exactly what King Hydros himself has said to me! / '''King Hydros:''' Ever since Alchemy was sealed away, the world has been cut off from its nourishment. It has gone into a state akin to hibernation.}}</ref>，加西亚便动身前去点燃木星灯塔。而当罗宾也追到木星灯塔上时，却中复仇心切的火元素使阿加迪奥和喀斯特的陷阱，加西亚帮助罗宾战胜了两名复仇者<ref name="felixsavesisaac">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''Sheba:''' But we're not leaving Isaac behind. / '''Karst:''' Oh, great... Are you going to betray us now? / '''Felix:''' Yes. / '''Karst:''' Typical. And you're going to try to stop us from finishing them off, aren't you? }}</ref>。在争议解决后，加西亚和罗宾会合并北方的火星灯塔进发<ref name="joinedtogether">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''Mia:''' I'm just relieved we've sorted out our differences. / '''Piers''' Me too, Mia... We could not have stood divided against a common foe. / '''Garet:''' Yeah, I guess I'm a little happy that we're not going to have to beat Felix up. / '''Isaac:''' Listen, this is Felix's quest now... We're just doing what we can to help out... }}</ref>；但是当加西亚到达火星灯塔塔顶时，贤者出现并警告队伍，若让人类拥有了如此强大的力量，世界将会被人类自己毁灭<ref name="riskofpower">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''The Wise One:''' If Alchemy is unleashed, mankind may well destroy all of Weyard itself. / '''Kraden:''' But we can combine our strengths, ensure that Alchemy not be used for evil... / '''The Wise One:''' It is inevitable. In time, one man will seek to rule over all. It is human nature, inescapable. And it shall come sooner than any of you think. }}</ref>。当明白罗宾执意要点燃灯塔后，贤者便召唤出来一条三头龙来作为最后的筹码<ref name="doomdragon">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''The Wise One:''' If you can defeat a miracle, only then can you ignite the beacon's flame. / '''Kraden:''' The Wise One is up to something! Be wary, everyone! We don't know what he's capable of! / '''Sheba:''' A three-headed dragon? '''That's''' your miracle? / '''Piers:''' So you would have us fight for our future? Fine, then fight we shall! }}</ref>。当队伍杀败三头龙并点燃火星灯塔点燃后，炼金术再度回到了维亚德，并聚集于阿尔法山上。而利用了其他人的阿历克斯只需站在阿尔法顶就能接受巨大的力量<ref name="alexusedeveryone">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''Jenna:''' Alex!? What would he be doing on Mt. Aleph? / '''The Wise One:''' He understands far more than you do. He knows that when the four beacons have been lit... Their light will gather at Sol Sanctum. / '''Kraden:''' But what would he gain from being there? / '''The Wise One:''' When the final beam of light reaches the peak of Mt.Aleph, the Golden Sun shall rise. / '''Kraden:''' The Golden Sun!? What is that? And what would Alex want with it? / '''The Wise One:''' When the four beams merge into one, they form a golden light, bathing Mt. Aleph's peak. / '''Ivan:''' Is... Is that Alchemy? I mean, pure Alchemy made real, at the heart of its power? / '''Kraden:''' And it's that light that gives shape to the Stone of Sages? / '''The Wise One:''' This has been Alex's one true desire from the very start. / '''Piers:''' Alex planned all this? Then he must have been after this power all along! / '''Garet:''' We've been duped! He used us all! Oh, you'd better believe he's not getting away with this!}}</ref>，然而正如贤者所料，阿历克斯随着坍塌的阿尔法山一起下沉了<ref name="mtalephdisappears">{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2003-04-14| platform=Game Boy Advance| language=en| quote= '''The Wise One:''' The heavens and earth are changing, Alex! You must flee now! / '''Alex:''' Wha-What!? / '''The Wise One:''' Mt.Aleph will soon be drawn into the heart of the earth! You must flee or join it forever! / '''Alex:''' Flee!? I can't flee! I can't even move! / '''The Wise One:''' Ah, yes. You now see the limits of your power. If you are swallowed by the earth, you may not survive. If you survive, perhaps we shall meet again someday...}}</ref>。

《[[黄金太阳_漆黑的黎明|漆黑的黎明]]》发生于《失落的时代》结局后的三十年。随着罗宾一行把黄金太阳之力重新带回了维亚德，大陆发生漂移，新的国家和物种诞生。然而，能吸取大自然和炼金术士精神力的精神力黑洞却出现在维亚德各处。特里意外的弄坏了伊万发明的滑翔翼，因而罗宾决定让他和穆特、卡莉丝一起到神鸟的岩山寻找修复材料——洛克鸟的羽毛<ref>{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=A Friend in Need| pages=19| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>。在途中他们遇到了反派斯派德、哈特<ref>{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=Kingdoms at War| pages=48| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>和艾斯<ref name="DDGuidepp41-42">{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=Konpa Ruins| pages=41-42| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>。穆特来到了兽人居住的摩尔格尔地区后就获得了洛克鸟的羽毛<ref>{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=No Mountain High Enough| pages=117| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>，同时他们也被骗启动了造成“被诅咒的日蚀”的露娜灯塔<ref>{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=Jail Break| pages=129| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>，而覆盖大半块大陆的日蚀之阴影带来了痛苦与死亡<ref>{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=Jail Break| pages=134| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>。为了终结日蚀，穆特等人击败了斯派德和哈特，并启动能增强炼金术机器输出的光之增幅机——阿波罗<ref>{{cite book| author=Stephen Stratton| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (eGuide)| year=2010| publisher=Prima Games| isbn=978-0-307-47107-9| chapter=The Endless Wall| pages=181-182| accessdate=2012-01-28| language=en}}</ref>。在启动了阿波罗，终结被诅咒的日蚀之后，一行人各自回到了家乡<ref>{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2010-11-29| platform=Nintendo DS| version=| level=| language=en| quote= '''Tyrell:''' But it's probably to get this feather home... / '''Eoleo:''' I guess I'll head home too, after I drop Himi off in Yamata. / '''Amiti:''' My countrymen no doubt await my return. I will leave shortly. / '''Rief:''' And what shall we do? / '''Karden:''' Whatever you think is best. From now on, you will learn not from me,but from the world. There are always new mysteries to solve. }}</ref>。然而，迎接穆特的却是一个异常巨大的精神力黑洞<ref>{{cite video game| title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn| developer=Camelot| publisher=Nintendo| date=2010-11-29| platform=Nintendo DS| version=| level=| language=en| quote= '''Karis:''' Ah, it's good to be back! / '''Matthew:''' (Point at a large Psynergy Vortex.)}}</ref>。

== 发展 ==

=== 开发史 ===

在最初，Camelot只计划将《黄金太阳》设计成一部而非系列，在最早期的设计文件中，游戏预定发布于[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]平台，但随着N64被[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]取代的迹象出现，Camelot便转而将精力投向掌机[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]平台<ref name="goldensun64">{{cite web |author=James Mielke |year=2008 |title=Previews: We Love Golf! |url=http://www.1up.com/do/previewPage?cId=3167178&p=44 |publisher=1up |accessdate=2008-04-13 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.fo/20121205225754/http://www.1up.com/previews/we-love-golf |archivedate=2012-12-05 }}</ref>。

《开启的封印》的开发周期为12至18个月，这段时间对于开发掌机游戏可以说很长了<ref name="development-time">{{cite web| author=IGN Staff| year=2001| title=Import Impressions: Golden Sun| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/097/097263p1.html| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2007-01-06| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ahb39z2F?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/08/08/import-impressions-golden-sun| archivedate=2012-09-15| df=}}</ref>，故而有人认为这是慢工出细活的“证明”<ref name="ignreview" />。在2000年8月日本举办的任天堂博览会上曾展出过一个《黄金太阳》试玩版<ref name="spaceworld" />。北美玩家在美版发布几周前就收到了游戏，IGN评论道：为世嘉开发[[光明系列|光明系列]]的经验帮助Camelot开发了一款精彩的掌机PRG<ref name="ign2prev">{{cite web| author=IGN staff| date=2001-11-02| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/099/099610p1.html| title=First Look: US Golden Sun| publisher=gbign.com| accessdate=2007-09-29| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ahb4cTZX?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/11/03/first-look-us-golden-sun| archivedate=2012-09-15| df=}}</ref>。

《失落的时代》日版发行于2002年，《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》杂志首先对游戏做出了评论<ref>{{cite web| author=Harris, Craig| date=2002-05-17| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/359/359732p1.html| title=Screens of Golden Sun 2| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-03-27| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVs38Ub?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/05/17/screens-of-golden-sun-2| archivedate=2012-10-05| df=}}</ref>。玩家对本作的发布高度期待，游戏排在了IGN 2003年度“最期待”GBA游戏的榜首<ref>{{cite web| author=Staff| date=2003-02-04| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/384/384939p1.html| title=Top 10 Most Wanted 2003/2004| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-03-27| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVsgrcI?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/02/04/top-10-most-wanted-20032004| archivedate=2012-10-05| df=}}</ref>。北美版曾在2002年[[E3游戏展|E3游戏展]]上展出<ref>{{cite web| author=Harris, Craig| date=2002-05-21| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/360/360275p1.html| title=E3 2002: First Look: Golden Sun 2| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-03-27| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVtMLfm?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/05/21/e3-2002-first-look-golden-sun-2| archivedate=2012-10-05| df=}}</ref>，[[IGN|IGN]]评论道：本作序章的对话不再像《开启的封印》一样枯燥，而是在动作过程中介绍人物<ref>{{cite web| author=Staff| date=2002-07-08| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/364/364225p1.html| title=Golden Sun 2: First Impressions| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-03-27| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BBVtwfQc?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2002/07/08/golden-sun-2-first-impressions| archivedate=2012-10-05| df=}}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]于2003年2月展示过一个英文化版，并评论道：游戏使用了前作的图像引擎，环境内容丰富，精细入微，例如鸟儿会在你靠近时飞走<ref>{{cite web|author=Torres, Ricardo |date=2003-02-28 |url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensunthelostage/news.html?page=1&sid=2911889&tag=result;title;0 |title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age Impressions |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2008-03-14 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207164129/http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensunthelostage/news.html?page=1&sid=2911889&tag=result%3Btitle%3B0 |archivedate=2008-12-07 }}</ref>。

《漆黑的黎明》最初由任天堂北美总裁[[雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米|雷吉·菲尔斯-埃米]]在2009年的任天堂E3游戏展上提及，称系列“曾在六年前走向黑暗，但现在将于[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]平台重新登陆”<ref>{{cite web| url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-10253732-235.html| title=Nintendo tries to regain the momentum| publisher=[[CNET|CNET]]| author=Terdiman, Daniel| date=2009-05-02| accessdate=2009-05-03| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090729174439/http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-10253732-235.html| archivedate=2009-07-29| df=}}</ref>。

在2012年6月Nintendo Gamer的采访中，游戏制作人高桥宏之表示：“我们制作RPG的一个重大原因就是来自喜欢我们RPG玩家的请求。若有足够的任天堂玩家希望我们制作另一部黄金太阳游戏，那我们就会再开发一作的。”<ref>{{cite web|title=Let Camelot Know If You Want Another Golden Sun|url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2012/06/let_camelot_know_if_you_want_another_golden_sun|publisher=Nintendo Life|accessdate=12 June 2012|author=James Newton|date=2012-06-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120630111551/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2012/06/let_camelot_know_if_you_want_another_golden_sun|archivedate=2012年6月30日|df=}}</ref>

=== 立意 ===

作为掌机游戏，《黄金太阳》最初只计划设计为一款游戏，但鉴于GBA卡带的容量有限，同时开发者亦有设计为两部之意，游戏最终得以成为连续的两作，即《开启的封印》和《失落的时代》<ref name="goldensun64" />。在编剧高桥宏之和监制高桥秀五设计的《[[光明力量III|光明力量III]]》中，游戏用了两个立场来讲述故事，也就是玩家将会控制“正派”和“反派”的角色。考虑到这是方法很适合衔接故事情节，因而在黄金太阳系列的设计中也是如此：即让玩家在《开启的封印》中控制正派，而在《失落的时代》中控制“反派”<ref name="gameplan">{{cite web| author=| year=2004| title=Rumor: Golden Sun for Gamecube?| url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/rumor/4522| publisher=Nintendo World Report| accessdate=2007-01-07| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ahb640pg?url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/rumor/4522| archivedate=2012-09-15| df=}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==

黄金太阳系列的主角罗宾也出现在了格斗游戏《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥X|任天堂明星大乱斗X]]》中，其身份中是需要来解锁的“出来乱一下人物”（{{lang-en|Assist Trophy}}），要在战斗中使用相应道具才能召唤出来。《大乱斗X》中的罗宾会通过“移动”精神力召唤出一只大手来推移其他人物，若敌人试图逃避，罗宾则将会紧追不舍<ref>{{cite web|author=Nintendo |date=2008-03-14 |url=http://www.smashbros.com/en_us/items/assist/assist16.html |title=Latecomer Assist Trophies |work=SmashBros.com |accessdate=2008-03-28 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080327232921/http://www.smashbros.com/en_us/items/assist/assist16.html |archivedate=2008-03-27 }}</ref>。此外，《失落的时代》组曲也被选进了《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥|大乱斗]]》的游戏音乐中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smashbros.com/en_us/music/music24_list.html |title=Hidden Music |work=SmashBros.com |accessdate=2008-03-28 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101032549/http://www.smashbros.com/en_us/music/music24_list.html |archivedate=2012-11-01 }}</ref>。

黄金太阳系列第一作的主角们还出现[[四格漫画|四格]][[同人_(ACG)|同人]]漫画《黄金太阳 开启的封印 4格趣味战》（{{lang|ja|黄金の太陽 開かれし封印 4コマギャグバトル}}）中，该漫画是[[光文社|光文社]]出版的火球游戏漫画系列（{{lang-ja|火の玉ゲームコミックシリーズ}}）的一部分。虽然该作品没有得到Camelot的正式许可，但因在日本，公司极少对未经正式授权而使用虚构角色的行为采取法律行动，故而日本同人志行业对此多是默-{}-认的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.akibaangels.com/doujin.php |title=What is Doujin? |publisher=Akiba Angels |accessdate=2010-12-17 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307153205/http://www.akibaangels.com/doujin.php |archivedate=2008-03-07 }}</ref>。该漫画以直行四格的方式排版，整个漫画由18名艺术家绘制成。

