黄金太阳系列获得了大量好评<ref name="reviews">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/g/game_boy_advance/golden_sun |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001000707/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/g/game_boy_advance/golden_sun |archivedate=2007-10-01 |title=Rotten Tomatoes review page |publisher=rottentomatoes.com |accessdate=2006-07-13 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。评论者称两作虽然只用了[[32位|32位]]的卡带<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web| date=2001-11-12| author=Torres, Ricardo| url=http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensun/review.html| title=Golden Sun for GBA- gamespot.com| publisher=gamespot.com| accessdate=2007-02-01| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070123125624/http://www.gamespot.com/gba/rpg/goldensun/review.html| archivedate=2007-01-23| df=}}</ref>，却能将绚丽的画面、高质的音效、多样而精致的设定以及非常有趣的精灵与战斗系统集于一身<ref name="goodreview1">{{cite web| url=http://www.gamerankings.com/gba/468548-golden-sun/index.html| title=Game Rankings- Golden Sun| publisher=Gamerankings.com| accessdate=2006-07-13| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305081644/http://www.gamerankings.com/gba/468548-golden-sun/index.html| archivedate=2009-03-05| df=}}</ref>。GamePro赞扬游戏道：《开启的封印》是“一款宏大的、奇妙的、富有创造性且十分有趣的RPG，而无需介怀其‘只是’一款GBA游戏”<ref name="reviews2">{{cite web| url=http://apps.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensun| title=Metacritic Game Rankings page| publisher=Metacritic.com| accessdate=2006-07-13| language=en| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720094940/http://apps.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/goldensun| archivedate=2011-07-20}}</ref>，而《失落的时代》也得到了“视觉效果远异于一般游戏”的好评<ref name="gamepro">{{cite web| url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/28950/golden-sun-the-lost-age/| title=Review: Golden Sun: The Lost Age| publisher=GamePro| accessdate=2008-04-11| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501185614/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/28950/golden-sun-the-lost-age/| archivedate=2009-05-01| df=}}</ref>。同时，IGN也称赞了系列“把游戏世界的各处都紧密结合在了一起”的剧情设定，玩家稍不留神就会迷失于丰富而有深度的剧情中<ref name="ignreview">{{cite web| author=Harris, Craig| date=2001-11-09| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/165/165255p1.html| title=IGN ''Golden Sun'' Review| publisher=ign.com| accessdate=2007-02-01| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AhazskzQ?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/11/10/golden-sun| archivedate=2012-09-15| df=}}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP]]也称赞《失落的时代》的画面流畅程度较前作更上了一层楼<ref name="dawn1up" />。

而前两作的战斗被指责不够“智能”，如果回合中预备攻击的敌人提前被杀，那么攻击该敌人的角色就会自动防御，而不是攻击其他人<ref name="gamepro" />。此外，也有批评声指游戏重复了“在地图上移动，随机遇敌，打赢随机战，继续在地图上移动，再次遇敌”的老路<ref name="thunder" />。而且他们也指出了过长的开篇对话会“赶走新的玩家”，还会“让玩家把游戏角色搞混”<ref name="gamespy rev">{{cite web|author=Padilla, Raymond |date=2004-04-26 |url=http://archive.gamespy.com/reviews/april03/goldensun2gba/ |title=Golden Sun: The Lost Age (GBA) |publisher=[[Gamespy|GameSpy]] |accessdate=2008-04-13 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080211094930/http://archive.gamespy.com/reviews/april03/goldensun2gba/ |archivedate=2008-02-11 }}</ref>。1UP批评Camelot迟迟未对剧情“减肥”，系列三作的对话都很冗长，主角和敌人之间本应很简单的对话能絮絮叨叨的重复三四遍<ref name="dawn1up">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/reviewPage?cId=3182572 |title=Golden Sun: Dark Dawn Review |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |author=Parish, Jeremy |date=2010-11-26 |accessdate=2010-12-17 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.fo/20120724163957/http://www.1up.com/reviews/golden-sun-dark-dawn-review |archivedate=2012-07-24 }}</ref>。[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]则对《漆黑的黎明》过于简单的难度而不满，称在主角“神速的升级”和精灵的狂轰滥炸面前，最终Boss实在是太弱<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/golden_sun_dark_dawn/b/nintendo_ds/archive/2010/12/06/return-to-a-lost-age-of-boring-storytelling-and-enjoyable-puzzle-solving.aspx| title=Return To A Lost Age Of Boring Storytelling And Enjoyable Puzzle-Solving| publisher=Game Informer| author=Kollar, Phil| date=2010-12-07| accessdate=2010-12-17| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210164728/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/golden_sun_dark_dawn/b/nintendo_ds/archive/2010/12/06/return-to-a-lost-age-of-boring-storytelling-and-enjoyable-puzzle-solving.aspx| archivedate=2010-12-10| df=}}</ref>。

《开启的封印》获得了2001年《任天堂力量》最佳GBA游戏奖，并排在IGN读者票选最佳100游戏的第94位<ref name="IGN Rankings" />，而在2007年GBA生命的尽头，《开启的封印》登上IGN举办的最佳25个GBA游戏的第24名<ref name="24th">{{cite web| author=Craig Harris| date=2007-03-16| year=2006| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/772/772284p1.html| title=Top 25 Game Boy Advance Games of All Time| publisher=IGN.com| accessdate=2007-03-18| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/69uHox7Ko?url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/772/772284p1.html| archivedate=2012-08-14| df=}}</ref>。此外，游戏由于“震撼的画质、音效，以及至少30小时的通关时间”而成为了IGN 2003年4月的月度游戏<ref>{{cite web| url=http://gameboy.ign.com/articles/400/400522p1.html| title=IGN:Game of the Month| publisher=IGN| date=2003-04-14| accessdate=2008-07-13| language=en| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AhbAMbYE?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/05/02/gba-game-of-the-month-april-2003| archivedate=2012-09-15| df=}}</ref>。

